import React from "react";

class Inputs extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Dados Pessoais</legend>
          <label for="nome">Nome:
            <input 
              type="text" 
              name="nome" 
              maxLength={4}  
              required 
              placeholder="Digite..." 
              autoComplete="off" 
            />
         </label>
         <label for="email">Email:
            <input 
              type="email" 
              name="email" 
              maxLength={50} 
              required 
              placeholder="Digite..." 
              autoComplete="off" 
            />
          
         </label>
      </fieldset>
    )
  }
}

export default Inputs
